Release 3.1.0-beta (Nov 13 2017)
============================
* Initial release of the new Connectome Mapper BIDS Manager

Release 3.0.1-beta (Jul 13, 2017)
=================================
* ENH: Refactored code (diffusion pipeline) to support current Nipype release
* ENH: Adoption of Brain Imaging Data Structure (BIDS) for input and derivatives data 
* ENH: Added Mrtrix3 preprocessing (dwidenoise, dwibiascorrec), reconstruction (dwi2response, tensor2metrics, dwi2fod), tracking (tckgen)
* ENH: Added option '-fsl_grad' to Mrtrix mrconvert interface
